                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  In the sequence of numbers $2, 3, 5, 8, 12, \ldots$, what is the first three digit number?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Let's find the difference between the consecutive terms of the sequence.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  The difference between the terms is increasing by 1 more than the difference between the previous numbers. Hence, the sequence would be:

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $ \begin{matrix} & \footnotesize{\maroonC{(+1)}} && \footnotesize{\maroonC{(+2)}}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  && \footnotesize{\maroonC{(+3)}}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  && \footnotesize{\maroonC{(+4)}} \ 2, && 3, && 5, && 8, && 12 \end{matrix} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Or it can also written as

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $2 + (1+2+3+4) =12$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  So,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $2 + (1 + 2 + 3 + 4 + 5 + 6 + 7 + 8 + 9) \ = 2 + 45 = 47$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $47 + (10 + 11 + 12 + 13 + 14) = 45 + 60 = 107$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  The first three digist number in the sequence will be $107$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $107$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  the-manchester-grammar-school--11-plus--maths--2013--arithmetic-1.toml

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  In a prod sequence, a number in the sequence is the product of some of the previous terms. So in a $2$ prod sequence we start with $2$ numbers and then each number that follows after is the product of the previous $2$ numbers.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  For example $1, 2, 2, 4, 8\ ...$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Similarly, where we start with the three numbers $1, 2$ and $3$ then a $3$ prod sequence would be

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $1, 2, 3, 6, 36, 648\ ...$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Fill in the missing numbers in the following sequences

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  TODOANSWER

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  TODOANSWER

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $2 \times 3 = 6$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $3 \times 6 = 18$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      The $2$ prod sequence is

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $2, \quad 3, \quad \underline {6}, \quad \underline {18}$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $6, \ 18$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • $3$ prod sequence

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $2, \quad 3, \quad 3, \quad \text{\textunderscore \textunderscore \textunderscore}, \quad \text{\textunderscore \textunderscore \textunderscore}$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $2 \times 3 \times 3 = 18$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $3 \times 3 \times 18 = 162$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        The $3$ prod sequence is

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $2, \quad 3, \quad 3, \quad \underline {18}\underline {162}$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          $2, \quad 3, \quad 5, \quad \text{\textunderscore \textunderscore \textunderscore}, \quad 210$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          $ \begin{aligned} 210 &= 2 \times 3 \times 5 \times x \ &= 30 \times x \text { or,}\\ x &= \dfrac {210}{30} \\ &= \dfrac{\cancel {210} \raisebox{0.9em}{7}} {\cancel {30}\raisebox{-0.9em}{1}}\\ x &= 7 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          The missing number is $7$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            $2, \quad \text{\textunderscore \textunderscore \textunderscore}, \quad \text{\textunderscore \textunderscore \textunderscore}, \quad \text{\textunderscore \textunderscore \textunderscore}, \quad 500$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Let's take the first missing number as $x$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            $2, \quad \underline x, \quad \underline {2 \times x}, \quad \underline {x \times 2 \times x}, \quad 500$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            $ \begin{aligned} 2x \times 2x \times 2x^2&= 500\ 2x \times 2x \times x^2 &= 500\ 4x \times x^2 &= 500 \ 4x^3 &= 500 \ x^3 &= \dfrac {500}{4} \\ x^3 &= \dfrac {500}{4} \ x^3 &= \dfrac {5 \times 100}{4} \ &= \dfrac{5 \times {\cancel {100} \raisebox{0.9em}{25}}} {\cancel {4}\raisebox{-0.9em}{1}}\\ &= 5 \times 25 &= 5^3 x &=5 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            $2, \quad 5, \quad \underline {10}, \quad \underline {50}, \quad 500$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              $ \begin{aligned} 3528 &= 2 \times x \times \times 7 \times (2 \times 2 \times \times x \times 7) \ &= (2 \times 7 \times 2 \times 2 \times \times 7) (x \times x \times) \ &= (2 \times 7 \times 2 \times 2 \times \times 7) (x^2) \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            What is the missing number in this list $33, 44, 56, \ldots, 83, 98$?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Let's find the difference between the consecutive terms of the sequence.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            $ \begin{matrix} & \footnotesize{\maroonC{(+11)}} && \footnotesize{\maroonC{(+12)}}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            && \footnotesize{\maroonC{(+13)}}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            && \footnotesize{\maroonC{(+14)}}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            && \footnotesize{\maroonC{(+15)}} \ 33, && 44, && 56, && \ldots, && 83, && 98 \end{matrix} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Write in the missing numbers of the sequence.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            The difference between the terms is $a$.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            $1$. ___, $9$, ___, ___

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            The difference between the terms is $a$.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            $ \begin{aligned} \text{First missing number} &= 1 \times a \\ &= 1 \times 3 \\ &= 3 \\ \text{Second missing number} &= 9 \times a \\ &= 9 \times 3 \\ &= 27 \text{Second missing number} &= 9 \times a \times a \\ &= 9 \times 3 \times 3 \\ &= 81 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • A sequence follows the rule: Treble and add one Explain why if the first term is $\frac{-2} {9}$ the second term is $\frac{1} {3}$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          As per the question, the next number in the sequence is tripled and added by one.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          If the first term is $\dfrac{-2} {9}$, then the next term would be : $ \begin{aligned} &= \dfrac{-2} {9} \times 3 + 1 \\ &= \dfrac {-2 \times 3} {3 \times 3} + 1 \\ &= \dfrac {-2 \times \cancel {3}} {3 \times \cancel {3}} + 1 \\ &= \dfrac{-2} {3} + 1 \\ &= \dfrac{-2} {3} + \dfrac{3} {3} \\ &= \dfrac{-2 + 3} {3} \\ &= \dfrac {1} {3} \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          The second term = $\dfrac {1} {3}$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          The second term = $\dfrac {1} {3}$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • Find the fourth term

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Let's find the difference between the consecutive terms of the sequence.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $ \begin{matrix} & \footnotesize{\maroonC{(\times 2)}} && \footnotesize{\maroonC{(\times 2)}} && \footnotesize{\maroonC{(\times 2)}} && \footnotesize{\maroonC{(\times 2)}} \ \box, && 3.5, && 7, && 14, && 28 \ldots \end{matrix} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $ \begin{aligned} \text{Missing number} \times 2 &= 3.5 \\ &= \dfrac {3.5} {2} \\ &= \dfrac {35} {20} \\ &= \dfrac {35 \times 5} {20 \times 5} \\ &= \dfrac {175} {100} \\ &= 1.75 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Missing number = $1.75$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    warwick-school--11-plus--maths--9999--sample-paper-1.toml

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    rag_ac_pr
